	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=25387"><span id=" ">StarChaser</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">3 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>For those of us looking for better storage in the bank, the new Deluxe Toolbox is perfect.&nbsp;&nbsp;It has 10 slots, holds items up to Giant, weighs 3.5 stones, and only costs around one and half plat or so depending on Charisma.  The only place in Norrath that you can buy one is at the Gnome Pirate Merchant in the igloos at the Icebreaker dock in Iceclad.  I bought several of them last night.  Not hard to get to and much better than the price of Sewing Kits or especially the hand crafted 10 slot backpacks.  For carrying things, you still can't beat the weight reduction bags, though.</p>&nbsp;<br /><span class=sm>----------------------------</span><br />StarChaser - Wood Elf Druid of the 43rd Season</td></tr>
